      "computation_method": "Immunohistochemistry or flow cytometry to detect FLS markers (e.g., CD90)."
    },
    {
      "name": "Pro-inflammatory Cytokine Panel",
      "value": 0,
      "description": "Concentrations of key cytokines (TNF-α, IL-6, IL-1β, IL-23) secreted by FLS following MMP inhibition.",
      "computation_method": "Multiplex bead-based assays (Luminex) or ELISA to measure cytokine levels."
    },
    {
      "name": "Osteoclast Differentiation Rate",
      "value": 0,
