    "score": 7,
    "justification": "The individual components (e.g., IL-23, MMPs, ECM degradation, osteoclastogenesis) are established in RA research, but combining them into one mechanistic cascade with particular emphasis on MMP-mediated ECM remodeling as a key step confers moderate novelty. The synergy of IL-23 and MMPs in this specific context is less commonly addressed in depth, though it builds on known pathways.",
