    "justification": "It provides a coherent mechanistic chain that accounts for both local joint erosion (via ECM degradation) and systemic features of bone loss through osteoclastogenesis, fitting a common phenotype in RA. It accounts for the interplay between inflammatory cells, synoviocytes, and bone cells, thus explaining why elevated IL-23 can accelerate joint and bone damage.",
